{"tid":1540480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭條7婆到底知唔知咩叫「五大訴求，缺一不可」","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:45:27.000Z","uid":316566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6cffa85828c25394c1d52a29b67362a77f170f53","tid":1540480,"uid":316566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:36:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">話說612之前<br />\n我同姐姐係到討論著咩衫去好<br />\n6月9主題係光明正大<br />\n大家都係着白色衫<br />\n6月12個時全民black bloc呢個概念都未係好流行<br />\n曾經有一刻我姐姐提出佢要著呢件野<br />\n（白灰色同款姊妹裝）<br />\n我嗰時仲用一個講笑嘅語氣話：「等階段性勝利先着啦！」<br />\n<br />\n去到今日逃犯條例撤回（按議事規則動議）<br />\n所謂既「階段性勝利」<br />\n香港人到底勝利左啲乜？<br />\n而家放棄點對得住犧牲左既手足啊？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U7Ek0L7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU7Ek0L7.png&h=f5e90b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">姐姐勿相認</span></span>"},{"pid":"f2a6045d72c06124abe9c384fc4313fff6944cfd","tid":1540480,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"全面抵制藍色餐廳<br />\n一齊打經濟戰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.289809900000016%252C114.1965917%26z%3D17&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvblcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=3827fc93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17</a>"},{"pid":"5b75989e0fb0e878abd541092627402c2382b17b","tid":1540480,"uid":287449,"like":0,"di